New trolleybuses

The new trolleybuses are equipped with the best conditions, have a very comfortable interior and protection against impacts in case of an accident. In addition, they are mostly used in the center of Europe. Especially in England and France.

Big trolleybuses

Large trolleybuses are mostly used in large cities, where there are a lot of residents of the country or tourists. Also used in the jungle for long trips. They do not have impact protection in the event of an accident.

Ordinary trolleybuses

Ordinary trolleybuses are used in small cities or not very wealthy countries. Ordinary trolleybuses are also available in Ukraine. Usually do not have any protection against shocks in the event of an accident.
